[00:00.800]--- lesson 21  Which book? 哪一本书？
[00:05.920]--- Listen to the tape then answer this question.^听录音，然后回答问题。
[00:12.160]--- Which book does the man want?^这位男士要哪本书？
[00:17.400]Give me a book please, Jane.^请拿本书给我，简。
[00:21.160]Which book?^哪一本？
[00:23.440]This one?^是这本吗？
[00:25.280]No, not that one.^不，不是那本。
[00:28.240]The red one.^是那本红皮的。
[00:30.240]This one?^这本吗？
[00:31.840]Yes, please.^是的，请给我。
[00:34.120]Here you are.^给你。
[00:36.000]Thank you.^谢谢。
[00:39.080]--- end